name: ''L0V3'' - Collectors Airdrop
description:
6months ago, I started my path in the #nftcommunity.
I’ve met so many incredible people, seen so much beautiful art and memes and together we are building our new world full of creativity and unstoppable passion. Together we laugh, we cry, we learn, we fight and most importantly we always support each other.
I want to celebrate this moment with you that always supported not only me but my art and dream too.
I feel very grateful and blessed. 
Thank you <3
